# CI/CD Pipeline for Flask App 🚀

This project demonstrates a CI/CD pipeline using **Jenkins**, **Docker**, and **GitHub**.

## 🔧 Tools Used
- Jenkins
- Docker & DockerHub
- GitHub
- Flask (Python 3.9)

## ⚙️ What This Does
- Builds a Docker image from this repo using Jenkins
- Runs tests (dummy for now)
- Pushes the image to DockerHub: `shripatil2001/my-app`
- Echoes a deploy step (can be replaced with a real deployment script)

